{"tid":612592,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人上水粉嶺走失左隻狗 個嘴帶狗口罩好慘","createTime":"2018-04-01T03:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T13:17:57.000Z","uid":124169,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2773c123b632138351c04239cb3db6822bb9e1bc","tid":612592,"uid":124169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/113722_dd7b55c1d77a9d68931c54178488582d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F113722_dd7b55c1d77a9d68931c54178488582d.png&h=d6605a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/113724_30add82f8098edd5dfcb1dab539179db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F113724_30add82f8098edd5dfcb1dab539179db.png&h=3017078e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身邊唔見有疑似主人蹤影<br />\n佢一路行一路頭dupdup搵野食咁<br />\n行過地下帶水就lam <br />\n可能餓/渴左好耐<br />\n有狗帶 似有人養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n帶狗口罩 如果真係走失<br />\n焗住流浪/被棄養 就好快餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我跟住佢行左半個鐘<br />\n佢越走越遠 最後唔敢再跟佢<br />\n驚佢離走失地點太遠 難搵返<br />\n我試過想幫佢除口罩<br />\n但我一蹲底/行近少少 佢就急急腳走<br />\n<br />\n點算 點幫到佢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802195d6cd716839bdb51127aa08ec104104c7db","tid":612592,"uid":34714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403af0c7263859802f4773af7b4fdb78a55dae62","tid":612592,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6ef140ecda7916243d8f62376a05dd